ces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e402a9f91dcbc48b5612a97dfc01e8f9a5dbaf25","tid":431113,"uid":57132,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T19:14:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171010/bkn-20171010223716852-1010_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171010%2Fbkn-20171010223716852-1010_00862_001.html&d=g9ZhlBacktmsfUCJb49Fi54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=62205184\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171010/bkn-20171010223716852-1010_00862_001.html</a><br />\n吳若希（Jinny）與老公Alex（何兆鴻）今日下午簽字註冊結婚，雖然沒有任何舖張儀式，甚至冇諗過大排筵席，但晚上Jinny跟老公與一班圈外好友就去銅鑼灣擦蟹慶祝，戴了口罩現身的Jinny跟老公繼續晒恩愛，兩人拖到實，心情靚到爆，對記者恭喜她，隔住個口罩都聽到Jinny哈哈的笑聲，<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然兩人已結婚，但Alex至今仍未向Jinny求婚，問到Alex打算拖到幾時，他尷尬笑說：「我一定會還。」</span>Jinny在旁邊勁笑說：「快啲逼佢！」<br />\n<br />\n感覺上何生真係唔係真心想娶佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd828e26f6e50703d10bf694a5d6f3a1a2fd9060","tid":431113,"uid":47433,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T19:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171010/bkn-20171010223716852-1010_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171010%2Fbkn-20171010223716852-1010_00862_001.html&d=g9ZhlBacktmsfUCJb49Fi54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=62205184\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171010/bkn-20171010223716852-1010_00862_001.html</a><br />\n吳若希（Jinny）與老公Alex（何兆鴻）今日下午簽字註冊結婚，雖然沒有任何舖張儀式，甚至冇諗過大排筵席，但晚上Jinny跟老公與一班圈外好友就去銅鑼灣擦蟹慶祝，戴了口罩現身的Jinny跟老公繼續晒恩愛，兩人拖到實，心情靚到爆，對記者恭喜她，隔住個口罩都聽到Jinny哈哈的笑聲，<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然兩人已結婚，但Alex至今仍未向Jinny求婚，問到Alex打算拖到幾時，他尷尬笑說：「我一定會還。」</span>Jinny在旁邊勁笑說：「快啲逼佢！」<br />\n<br />\n感覺上何生真係唔係真心想娶佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都結咗婚仲求乜撚嘢婚<img src=\"/asset